title: Educator Advanced PHP with MySQL
description:
Duration 15 hours mp4

Matthew Machaj's Advanced PHP with MySQL course continues from his Introduction to PHP course but is also appropriate for those already well versed in PHP. Matthew again focuses on topics relevant to developers and works on real code in text editors as well as executing MySQL commands from the command prompt. A working web application program will also be developed throughout the course to build on new concepts learned. Topics covered include reading/writing files, object-oriented programming, cookies, MySQL databases, and MySQL commands
